{"tid":1107733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"壽司有蟲話俾我哋知，好多事其實表面俾「我話OK就OK」掩蓋住","createTime":"2019-04-15T12:40:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T05:25:26.000Z","uid":64694,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5e76dc6e9b927c394c5a441ead06518f3aeecb27","tid":1107733,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:40:52.000Z","msg":"其實我哋生活入面身邊好多嘢係潛在有問題，但係只係我哋唔知<br />\n<br />\n政府、大企業會用「我話OK就OK」呢句嘢令我哋放低戒心，實際上可能只係為咗冚住件事唔俾人知，好似咩鉛水、沙中線剪鋼筋、壽司有蟲、遺失選民登記冊等等，俾人揭發先自己認咗佢，有啲比較賤嘅就唔認，好似東張西望影到臭豆腐檔嘢，明明影晒都可以唔認，有啲重要賤格到唔認不特止，重要走去告揭發條友，就好似Theranos事件一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab501fc4a492a5d13bd920ffacd219386a6c8d8","tid":1107733,"uid":64694,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:48:24.000Z","msg":"醫療界及初創公司的世紀大騙局 Theranos 成魔之路 離奇過小說<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/culture/aby5n5g.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fculture%2Faby5n5g.html&d=hmtFoPnP%2FIv5fOqUL3ZUajYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=519acdc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/culture/aby5n5g.html</a>"},{"pid":"6cfd386dea64918d5d81e7d7306889baa26fb348","tid":1107733,"uid":232594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:20:57.000Z","msg":"間野愈大間影響力愈勁就愈多仆街野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5643fe535d949a36047d8d54ca13ce9f63a1e5e","tid":1107733,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:22:10.000Z","msg":"從來唔幫襯美心集團旗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3760c14fa006044cdf431fdee8c812cac583e1","tid":1107733,"uid":16676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:23:00.000Z","msg":"人大831 決定<br />\n引渡條例"},{"pid":"1b20fe1310fd715928d115535b28a4a8d1c106d8","tid":1107733,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:23: